    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:var(--surface-dark);background-color:var(--surface-dark);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"position: absolute; background: var(--texture-grain); opacity: 0.04; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:var(--space-10) var(--space-6) var(--space-10);display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0\"><div style=\"width: var(--space-7); height: var(--space-7); background: #E24F8212; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: var(--space-3); margin: 0 0 16px;\">\ud83e\uddec</div><h2 style=\"font-family: Playfair Display; font-size: 25px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.12; color: #F5ECEE; margin: 0 0 var(--space-1); text-align: left; letter-spacing: -0.015em; overflow-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"color:#E24F82;font-weight:800;margin-right:12px;font-family:Playfair Display;\">01</span>The Composition Engine</h2><p style=\"font-family: DM Sans; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.55; color: #D7CACD; margin: 0; text-align: left\">Nexus doesn&#x27;t pick slides randomly. It composes \u2014 selecting each slide type based on the emotional position in the narrative arc, the content density of the brief, and the target audience&#x27;s cognitive load budget.</p></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
    "background": "dark",
    "variant": "stacked",
    "theme": "bold",
    "archetype": "thought_leader",
    "slide_type": "feature"
  },
  {
    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:var(--surface-dark);background-color:var(--surface-dark);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"background: var(--texture-grain); position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.04; z-index: 1\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:80px var(--space-6) 80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-start;\">\n            <div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:230px;border-radius:var(--radius-md);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);border:1px solid #3B282C30;\">\n                <div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:240px;border-radius: var(--radius-sm);overflow:hidden;background:transparent;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?w=600\" alt=\"Annotated Diagram\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit: cover; object-position: center;filter: contrast(1.06) brightness(1.06);\" />\n                \n            </div>\n                \n            </div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:12px;color:#D7CACD;margin:10px 0 0;line-height:1.45;opacity:0.9;\">Every visual element is computed, not hardcoded.</p>\n            <div style=\"margin-top:10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;width:100%;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:12px;color:#D7CACD;line-height:1.45;\">\n                        <strong style=\"color:#F5ECEE;font-weight:700;\">Dynamic font scaling</strong> \u2014 Text sizes adjust based on content density \u2014 dense slides get smaller type, sparse slides breathe\n                    </div><div style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:12px;color:#D7CACD;line-height:1.45;\">\n                        <strong style=\"color:#F5ECEE;font-weight:700;\">Theme token system</strong> \u2014 Material Design 3 tonal palette with per-preset color overrides\n                    </div></div>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
    "background": "dark",
    "variant": "default",
    "theme": "bold",
    "archetype": "data_analyst",
    "slide_type": "image_callout"
  },
  {
    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:radial-gradient(at 40% 20%, #AD145715 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 80% 0%, #007E6910 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 0% 50%, #FF76A712 0px, transparent 50%), var(--surface-light);background-color:var(--surface-light);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"background: var(--texture-grain); pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.04; z-index: 1; inset: 0; position: absolute\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:80px var(--space-6) 80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-family: Playfair Display; font-size: 25px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.12; color: #0F090B; margin: 0 0 12px; text-align: left; letter-spacing: -0.015em; overflow-wrap: break-word\">How Composition Works</h2>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;width:100%;\"><div style=\"min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #D0C3C6;border-radius:0;padding:14px 14px 12px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;\">\n                <div style=\"width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:#AD1457;color:#FFF1F4;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;\">01</div>\n                <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#0F090B;margin-bottom:2px;\">Brief Analysis</div>\n                    <div style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#4A3F42;line-height:1.4;\">NLP extracts topic, tone, audience, and intent from natural language</div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div style=\"min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #D0C3C6;border-radius:0;padding:14px 14px 12px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;\">\n                <div style=\"width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:#AD1457;color:#FFF1F4;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;\">02</div>\n                <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#0F090B;margin-bottom:2px;\">Arc Selection</div>\n                    <div style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#4A3F42;line-height:1.4;\">Matches intent to one of 7 emotional arc categories across 28 presets</div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div style=\"min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #D0C3C6;border-radius:0;padding:14px 14px 12px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;\">\n                <div style=\"width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:#AD1457;color:#FFF1F4;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;\">03</div>\n                <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#0F090B;margin-bottom:2px;\">Slide Sequencing</div>\n                    <div style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#4A3F42;line-height:1.4;\">Selects slide types that advance the arc, enforcing DLD rhythm and variety constraints</div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div style=\"min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #D0C3C6;border-radius:0;padding:14px 14px 12px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;\">\n                <div style=\"width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:#AD1457;color:#FFF1F4;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0;\">04</div>\n                <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#0F090B;margin-bottom:2px;\">Visual Rendering</div>\n                    <div style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#4A3F42;line-height:1.4;\">Each slide compiles with dynamic typography, theme tokens, and content-adaptive layout</div>\n                </div>\n            </div></div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:10.5px;color:#4A3F42;margin:4px 0 0;line-height:1.4;opacity:0.85;\">Automated 3-step compilation pipeline converting raw JSON specifications into production-ready carousel assets.</p>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
    "background": "light",
    "variant": "process_map",
    "theme": "editorial",
    "archetype": "educator",
    "slide_type": "process_map"
  },
